ABOUT_US_DOCTOR_SECTION1_P1: Joyina ukunyakaza ukuhlinzeka ngokuthembeka, okungabizi, ukufinyelela emhlabeni wonke ekunakekelweni kwezempilo kungakapheli imizuzu engu-15 noma ngaphansi.
ABOUT_US_DOCTOR_SECTION1_P2: I-Saluber MD iklanyelwe ukuguqula ubudlelwane nodokotela-mgulane ngokwenza ukufinyelela kwe-24/7 ekunakekelweni kwezempilo emhlabeni wonke.
about_us_section1_p1: I-SaluberMD iyinhlangano ye-Digital Health eyenzelwe ukuguqula ukulethwa kwezinsizakalo zezokwelapha nemikhiqizo ukuthuthukisa imiphumela yezempilo emhlabeni jikelele. Izinsizakalo zethu ze-Digital Medical Concierge, zinikeza ukufinyelela kwezinzuzo zezempilo nempilo, odokotela bebhodi abaqinisekisiwe, ifayela lezokwelapha siqu ngezilimi ezingu-18, izingubo zokugqoka zokuqapha impilo yakho, nokufinyelela kwinethiwekhi yabaqeqeshi bezempilo kanye nezinsizakalo.
ABOUT_US_SECTION2_P1:
Ngokusebenzisa i-geo-localization uhlelo lwethu lokusebenza luzothola Udokotela ongcono kakhulu eduze kwakho. I-SaluberMD Physicians ingakwazi ukuxilonga, ukuphatha noma ukuxoxa ngesimo sakho sezokwelapha ngevidiyo futhi ikunikeze uhlelo olufanele lwezokwelapha. Izimo eziningi ezivame ukwelashwa ehhovisi likadokotela zingaphathwa ngokuvakashelwa kwevidiyo.
Ezinye zezimo esiziphathayo:
ABOUT_US_SECTION2_P2: Ikhompiyutha Yakho Yezokwelapha yindawo elula yokugcina yonke idatha yakho yezempilo, izithombe namafayela. Gcina ithrekhi yempilo yakho ngokufinyelela kwama-24/7 kuwo wonke amarekhodi akho ezokwelapha. Kungakhathaliseki ukuthi uhlala ekhaya noma uhamba ngaphandle kolwazi lwakho kutholakale kalula ukuze wabelane nochwepheshe wezempilo. I-easy to use rekodi yezokwelapha yomuntu siqu iyatholakala ngezilimi ezingu-18.
ABOUT_US_SECTION3_P1: Kuphela odokotela abaqinisekisiwe bebhodi abahlinzeka ngokuhlinzekwa ngezokwelapha ku-SaluberMD. Labachwepheshe baqinisekiswa, bahlolwe kakhulu futhi baqeqeshwe ukuhlinzeka ukunakekelwa kwekhwalithi ephezulu. Udokotela ngamunye une-bio lapho ungabuka khona imvelaphi yabo, iziqinisekiso, nesipiliyoni. I-SaluberMD izinikele ekuphathweni kwekhwalithi eqhubekayo yabangcali bethu. Isistimu yokulinganisa ivumela iziguli ukuba zilinganise odokotela futhi zibheke odokotela jikelele isilinganiso.

PRICING_SECTION1_P1: I-SaluberMD izinikele ekuhlinzekeni ukunakekelwa okulula, kwekhwalithi ngamanani angabizi futhi akukho mali efihlekile noma amacala.
PRICING_SECTION1_P2: I-SaluberMD inikeza ukunakekelwa nomaphi noma nini lapho uyidinga ngevidiyo ukuvakashela nodokotela oqinisekisiwe webhodi. Odokotela bethu bangaxoxa, bahlole futhi balalele ukuxilonga izinkinga zakho noma bamane ubhekane nemibuzo yezokwelapha nokukhathazeka ngenkathi ushayele ikholi yevidiyo.
PRICING_SECTION1_P3: Nge-Medicfile yethu ekhethekile unganikeza udokotela wakho ukufinyelela emlandweni wakho wezokwelapha, izithombe zakho namafayela ukuzisiza ukuthi zinikeze uhlelo olusebenzayo kakhulu yokwelashwa.
QUALITY_INDEX_DESCRIPTION: Ukuqina komzimba yizinga lokuqina nokucindezeleka kwengqondo okuhlangene nakho kokukwazi ukujwayela nokubhekana nesimo. Inkomba yempilo yomzimba ibonisa umzimba womuntu ukuvumelanisa nezinguquko zemvelo nokucindezeleka ukuvuselela, ukugcina nokubuyisela ikhono lempilo. Ukuzivocavoca umzimba kuvame ukubonakaliswa ngokusemandleni okuphila kwabantu, ukufunda nokusebenza, kodwa futhi ngokwemvelo ekuzivocavoca umzimba. Ikhwalithi yomzimba yomuntu ihlobene nokuzalwa kodwa isondelene kakhulu nokuthola ukudla okunomsoco nokuzivocavoca umzimba. Ngezindlela ezifanele nokuzivocavoca okufanele, angakwazi ukuthuthukisa ukuqina kwakhe ngokomzimba kuzo zonke izici.
QUESTIONS_SECTION_TITLE: Thola ukubonisana okukhululekile noma ucingo lwezempilo ngemuva kokugcwalisa ngokuphelele ifayela lakho lezokwelapha.
RECOMMEND_SECTION_P1: E-SaluberMD silwela ukuhlangabezana nesidingo sokunakekelwa kwezempilo okusezingeni quality ngokunikeza amakhasimende ethu ukufinyelela eqenjini elihle elihle labasebenzi.
RECOMMEND_SECTION_P2: Siso sonke sifuna ikhwalithi Abahlengikazi ukungeza eqenjini lethu elimangalisayo. Njengelungu lethimba lethu sihlonipha futhi sibaluleka ukuthumela kwakho.
RECOMMEND_SECTION_P3: Sicela ugcwalise ifomu elingezansi ukuze ubheke udokotela ku-SaluberMD

rr_desc: Isilinganiso sokuphefumula yisilinganiso lapho ukuphefumula kwenzeka khona. Izinga lokuphefumula elijwayelekile lomuntu omdala ekuphumula liyi-12 kuya ku-20 ukuphefumula ngomzuzu. Izinga lokuphefumula ngaphansi kuka-12 noma ngaphezulu kwempumulo engu-25 ngomzuzu ngenkathi ukuphumula kubhekwa njengokwejwayelekile
sai_desc: I-SAI isekelwe ngokulinganisa kwenhliziyo yakho. I-metric elula elandelela impendulo yomzimba emisebenzini yomzimba - okungaphezulu nje kwezinyathelo. Ngokungafani nokulandela izinyathelo, i-SCI inikeza isikweletu ngemisebenzi yonke ephakamisa izinga lenhliziyo: ukubhukuda, ukuhamba ngebhayisikili, ukugoqa, ukudansa, noma yini. Gcina ngezansi kwe-30 impilo engcono neyimpilweni.
sbpi_desc: Umfutho wegazi ophakeme ngumbulali othulile. Amanani akho wegazi we-Systolic ne-Diastolic acatshangwa phakathi naleso sigaba sezokwelapha owenzayo. Gcina i-SBPI engaphansi kuka-30 ukuba nethuba eliphansi lokuhlupheka ngenxa yezimo zokusongela impilo ezifana nesifo sohlangothi kanye negazi.
sci_desc: Ngokuhlaziya amagagasi wakho we-pulterial pulse sithola ulwazi mayelana nesistimu yakho ye-cardiovascular. Inkomba ye-SCI isishwankathelo sempilo yakho yesifo senhliziyo, zama ukuyigcina ngezansi kwe-20!

sii_desc: I-SII iyinhlanganisela yazo zonke izinhlamvu zeSaluberMD futhi yisibuko sengozi yakho jikelele yezokwelapha. Uma ungaphansi kuka-30 usendaweni ephephile!

spo2_desc: I-SpO2 noma i-blood oxygen level isilinganiso sokuthi ingakanani amangqamuzana egazi obomvu aphetheyo. Amanani avamile aphakathi kuka-95% no-100%, A ngezansi-evamile igazi oksijeni level kuthiwa i-hypoxemia
sri_desc: Sihlaziya indlela yakho yokuphefumula nganoma isiphi isikhathi sezokwelashwa nangesikhathi sokulala kwakho. Uma i-SRI ingaphansi kuka-30 amathuba akho okuhlupheka ngenxa yezimo zokuphefumula ezivimbelayo ziphansi.
ssi_desc: Ngokuhlaziya ukuhluka kwesimo senhliziyo sakho silinganisa izinga lakho lokucindezeleka. Ukucindezeleka kubonakala kubi kakhulu noma kwandisa ingozi yezimo ezinjengokukhuluphala, isifo senhliziyo, isifo se-Alzheimer, isifo sikashukela, ukucindezeleka, izinkinga zomzimba kanye nesifo se-asthma. Gcina ngezansi kwe-20 ukuba ube ohlangothini oluphephile!

subject: Isihloko
temperDescription: Isilinganiso esingokomzwelo esihlanganisa uhla lwesikhala sonke sesikhulumi. Ulaka oluphansi luchaza imizwa yokucindezeleka nokukhathazeka. Intukuthelo enembile ichaza imizwelo enobungane, efudumele neyamukelekayo. Amagugu aphakeme kakhulu achaza imizwelo yokuhlukumezeka, yokuphatha nokuhlukumezeka.

tipshealt10: Chofoza lapha ukuze uthole olunye ulwazi
tipshealt11: Izinzuzo zokwelashwa kwesimiso, izidakamizwa ezinciphisa i-cholesterol, zidlula izingozi
tipshealt12: Esihlokweni sokubuyekezwa kwamuva kuLancet, abacwaningi baphetha ngokuthi izinzuzo zokunciphisa i-cholesterol ye-LDL ne-statin therapy zingase zivimbele izenzakalo ezinkulu ze-vascular (ukuhlaselwa yinhliziyo, ukushaya) futhi kukhulu kakhulu izingozi zezidakamizwa.
tipshealt13: Ngokusho kwabacwaningi izenzakalo ezimbi ezimbi eziye zaboniswa ukuthi zibangelwa ukwelashwa kwe-statin isikhathi eside yi-myopathy (echazwa ngokuthi ubuhlungu besisu noma ubuthakathaka), isifo sikashukela esisha esisha, futhi, mhlawumbe, isifo esiwumshayabhuqe.
tipshealt2: Nakuba umgomo wokugoma awuhlali njalo uhlinzeka ukuvikelwa okuphelele, kufanelekile ukuthola. I-CDC (Izikhungo Zokulawula Nokuvimbela Izifo) incoma imishanguzo yonyaka wamagciwane wonke umuntu oneminyaka eyi-6 noma ngaphezulu. Ukugoma kubaluleke kakhulu kubantu abasengozini enkulu yemithonya yemfuluwenza, kuhlanganise
tipshealt5: Izingane ezincane (ngaphansi kweminyaka engama-4 nangaphezulu kwezinyanga ezingu-6)
tipshealt6: Umsebenzi womzimba uthuthukisa inkumbulo namakhono okucabanga
tipshealt7: Umsebenzi wokuzivocavoca njalo ungathuthukisa ukusebenza kobuchopho phakathi nempilo yonke futhi kunciphise ingozi yokugula komqondo.
tipshealt8: Ucwaningo oluningi luye lwashicilelwa ekusebenzisaneni okusheshayo futhi kunenzuzo yokusebenza ngokomzimba njalo nokusebenza kwengqondo okuthuthukisiwe.
tipshealt9: Ithonya liqondiswe ngokuqondile ebuchosheni futhi ngokungaqondile ngokusebenzisa izenzo zamathambo nezomzimba emzimbeni.
